text: The Hôpital André-Mignot is a hospital in France. It is in the commune of Le Chesnay, close to Paris. It was created in 1981.L'hôpital Mignot a 30 ans It is a partner of the Université de Versailles Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines.UFR Simone Veil - santé == References == == Further reading == * Hôpital André- Mignot Category:1980s establishments in France Category:1981 establishments in Europe Category:University hospitals in France Category:Yvelines
